    blurb: "One of the island's largest private estates — eight oversized en-suite bedrooms across 1,808 m² of build on a 2,164 m² freehold headland plot above Choeng Mon, with panoramic ocean views, an infinity pool, twin kitchens and resort-scale entertaining space. Fully furnished and move-in ready.",
    detail: "Set on an elevated headland in the prestigious Choeng Mon area, this is a rare mega-estate built for grand-scale living. Across 1,808 m² of built area on a 2,164 m² freehold Chanote plot, the home pairs unmatched scale with premium craftsmanship — high ceilings, expansive open-plan rooms and floor-to-ceiling glass framing sweeping views over the Gulf of Thailand.\n\nEight oversized bedrooms each have private en-suite bathrooms and in-room comforts, with ten bathrooms in total giving flexibility for large families, multi-generational stays or a high-yield luxury rental operation. Two fully equipped kitchens serve both everyday life and professional catering, while a grand lounge anchors the home alongside multiple TV and relaxation rooms for privacy and entertaining.\n\nOutdoor living centres on a large infinity pool and generous terraces, all oriented to capture the panoramic Choeng Mon seascape. Turnkey furnishings, government power and water, a private transformer, smart-home systems and a gated, secured setting complete a move-in-ready estate — minutes from Choeng Mon Beach, Chaweng, Fisherman's Village and Samui International Airport.",
