    blurb: "One of Koh Samui's most prestigious private residences — a seven-bedroom, resort-scale estate set on 9,600 m² of freehold Chanote land high on the tranquil southwest coast at Taling Ngam, famed for its sunsets. Sweeping panoramic sea views, landscaped grounds and a full suite of resort amenities — a fully equipped gym, private spa, full-size tennis court and Thai-style salas — make this a rare trophy property. Seven en-suite bedrooms, eight bathrooms, fully furnished and move-in ready.",
    detail: "This extraordinary seven-bedroom estate is one of the island's most prestigious private residences, offering an unrivalled combination of privacy, expansive land and world-class amenities in one of Koh Samui's most exclusive coastal areas. Set on an impressive 9,600 m² of freehold Chanote land, it delivers a level of space rarely found on the island, with sweeping panoramic sea views, beautifully landscaped grounds and luxury facilities throughout — a home designed for buyers seeking the very highest level of tropical living.\n\nTaling Ngam is widely regarded as one of Koh Samui's most exclusive and tranquil areas, known for its breathtaking sunset views, natural landscapes and luxury private estates; properties of this scale and quality are extremely rare. The residence pairs seven spacious bedrooms with eight bathrooms, offering exceptional capacity for family and guests while the expansive layout keeps privacy intact across elegant living and entertainment spaces. Ownership is freehold under Chanote title — the highest level of land ownership in Thailand — providing maximum long-term security.\n\nDesigned as a true luxury retreat, the estate includes an impressive range of resort-style facilities: a fully equipped gym, a private spa area and a full-size tennis court create a complete wellness and recreation environment within the privacy of the grounds. Outdoor areas include beautifully maintained tropical gardens, large lawns and traditional Thai-style salas, perfect for relaxation, outdoor dining and entertaining, while the interiors support both elegant hosting and comfortable everyday living with spacious lounges, dining spaces and private bedroom suites. Generous parking, laundry areas and well-planned infrastructure support the scale of the home, with reliable government electricity and water.\n\nLocated on the peaceful southwest coast, the estate enjoys a quieter, more exclusive atmosphere than the island's busier zones, yet remains within comfortable driving distance of Lipa Noi Beach, five-star resorts, fine dining and Samui International Airport. With its massive land size, panoramic sea views, luxury amenities and resort-style design, it stands among the most unique properties currently available on Koh Samui. Offered freehold under Chanote title, fully furnished and move-in ready — priced at ฿400,000,000.",
