    blurb: "A modern multi-level villa perched in the Chaweng Noi hills with a wraparound terrace and an infinity pool framing Chaweng Beach and Koh Phangan beyond — four en-suite king bedrooms, a private cinema and a games room with full bar. 520 m² of build on a 708 m² plot — freehold, move-in ready.",
    detail: "Perched majestically in the prestigious Chaweng Noi hills, this contemporary four-bedroom villa is a study in indoor-outdoor island living, opening to panoramic views that sweep from the vibrant curve of Chaweng Beach to the serene silhouette of Koh Phangan. A wide cantilevered terrace and an infinity-edge pool anchor the home, with a vast sun deck, daybeds and a covered sanctuary for shaded afternoons above the sea.\n\nInside, a large air-conditioned living space is layered with plush seating and wall-mounted screens, flowing to a fully equipped Western show kitchen. Entertainment runs deep: a private cinema, a games room with pool, ping-pong and foosball tables, a full-size arcade and an in-house bar, plus Sonos throughout, a stocked wine fridge and a garden with a tranquil waterfall.\n\nFour en-suite double bedrooms each have king beds, and the master enjoys spectacular sea views from one of the largest bathrooms on the island. The home delivers 520 m² of build on a 708 m² plot with covered parking, sold freehold and move-in ready. Chaweng Noi beach is a five-minute walk, with restaurants, bakeries and shops moments away — and the position makes the villa equally suited to private ownership or a premium rental program.",
