    added: 60, ownership: "Freehold",
    blurb: "A private estate set across seven rai of elevated hillside above Chaweng, where seven en-suite bedrooms, generous open living spaces and an infinity pool look out over the Gulf of Thailand. Fully furnished and turnkey, on a scale of land rarely found this close to the island's lifestyle hubs — freehold, Chanote, move-in ready.",
    detail: "It is unusual to find this much land — seven rai — held in one piece so close to Chaweng. That space is the estate's first luxury: a sense of privacy and quiet that comes from being set back and lifted above the coast, with landscaped gardens and open ground on every side. The elevated position does the rest, drawing refreshing breezes across the house and opening sweeping views over the Gulf of Thailand from the living areas, the bedrooms and the pool terrace alike.\n\nSeven en-suite bedrooms make room for large families, gathered friends or a premium rental program, with two additional children's rooms suited to multi-generational stays. The plan is built around open living spaces that connect directly to the outdoors, embracing the indoor-outdoor rhythm of island life. At its heart sits an infinity pool set along the edge of the terrace, positioned to hold the horizon and the coastline below, with generous deck space for shade, sun and long evenings as the light goes down.\n\nDelivered fully furnished, the residence is ready to enjoy or to place into rental from day one. Government electricity and water supply the home, parking is generous, and the freehold Chanote title offers the strongest form of ownership available — a rare combination of scale, position and security in one of Koh Samui's most sought-after hillside settings, minutes from Chaweng Beach, Fisherman's Village and the airport.",
