    detail: "An exceptional 2-rai beachfront plot in Taling Ngam — a rare chance to acquire freehold property on one of Koh Samui's most serene and picturesque coastlines. With a direct beachfront position and breathtaking views of the turquoise Gulf of Thailand, the land suits a luxury private villa, a small collection of high-end villas, or a boutique resort, in an exclusive and tranquil part of the island.\n\nThe parcel measures 2 rai (3,200 m²), offering ample space for a large private estate with infinity pools, outdoor living areas and landscaped tropical gardens. Its gentle slope and natural elevation enhance the sea views while keeping construction straightforward, and direct beach frontage makes it one of the most versatile coastal offerings currently available on the island.\n\nTaling Ngam is renowned for its pristine coastline, dramatic sunsets and authentic island charm. Unlike the busier resort areas, the region remains unspoiled, protecting the privacy and exclusivity of properties here. Within a short drive are the famous Five Islands viewpoint, the InterContinental resort and beachside seafood restaurants, while Samui International Airport and the busier areas of Lamai and Chaweng are about thirty minutes away. Offered freehold under Chanote title, with private transformer and deep-well water in place.",
