    detail: "One of the most exclusive opportunities currently available on the island — a dual beachfront villa estate in Maenam, comprising two separate luxury villas sold together on a substantial 3,200 m² plot with direct beach access and a combined ~42 metres of prime beach frontage. The scale, privacy and irreplaceable beachfront positioning suit ultra-high-net-worth buyers, family compounds, boutique wellness retreats or luxury hospitality concepts.\n\nVilla One holds seven bedrooms and nine bathrooms, a private gym, a sauna, a conference/meeting room, timber ceilings throughout, large BBQ and entertainment areas, a 15 × 5-metre swimming pool and approximately 23 metres of direct beach frontage. Villa Two holds seven bedrooms and seven bathrooms, its own 15 × 5-metre pool and roughly 19 metres of frontage. Both are designed to operate independently or as a single private estate — flexible for personal use, staff accommodation or high-end rental.\n\nThe estate delivers a full resort-style living experience, with wellness and lifestyle facilities including the gym and sauna and generous outdoor entertainment spaces ideal for events, retreats or extended family stays. The dedicated conference room further enhances its versatility for executive retreats, wellness programmes and luxury corporate rentals — an increasingly in-demand segment of the Samui market.\n\nMaenam is widely regarded as one of Koh Samui's most desirable beachfront locations, with long stretches of natural sand, calm swimming and a relaxed yet upscale atmosphere, within easy reach of Fisherman's Village, international schools, golf and Samui International Airport. Absolute beachfront plots of this size and frontage are extremely limited, making this estate a true legacy asset. Offered freehold, fully furnished and move-in ready — priced at $13,000,000.",
