    blurb: "Branded pool villas and condominiums set on a lush, ocean-facing hillside within a celebrated five-star resort in Layan Bay — just 42 residences across 100 rai, steps from Layan Beach. Three- and four-bedroom homes from 251 to 829 m², each with a private pool, plus access to the resort's spa, restaurants, beach club, helipad and yacht jetty. Freehold, off-plan.",
    detail: "A luxury branded residential development of just 42 private pool villas and condominiums in Layan Bay, on the north-west coast of Phuket — spaciously allotted over 100 rai (40 acres) of lush, ocean-facing hillside, steps from Layan Beach and adjacent to two existing ultra-luxury residences and a celebrated five-star resort. Set within the resort itself, the homes share its grounds, services and hotel-standard maintenance, with planned future expansion expected to lift both lifestyle and value over time.\n\nThe collection is composed of 17 three- and four-bedroom villas of 501 to 655 m², and 25 three- and four-bedroom condominiums — single-storey, duplex and penthouse layouts ranging from 251 to 829 m². Every villa and condominium has its own private pool. Interiors are generous and resort-grade, conceived for indoor-outdoor living against the hillside and ocean backdrop.\n\nOn-site facilities include a residents-only swimming pool, fitness centre, club house and parking, while the wider resort opens up Thai and international restaurants, a renowned spa, beachside dining and a rooftop bar at the beach club, an active sport-and-leisure zone, and an on-site helipad and yacht tender jetty. Ownership comes with a rental programme operated by the hotel group's real-estate team and exclusive privileges across its global hotel and loyalty networks.\n\nThe setting is the rare draw: serene, green Layan, with the resort's beach frontage and beach club at your doorstep, Layan Beach just 600 metres away, the Laguna resort district a couple of kilometres on, and Boat Avenue and Porto de Phuket around fifteen minutes' drive — Phuket International Airport is roughly twenty-five minutes. Offered freehold within a hotel development, with attractive terms of just 10% down and 70% payable on handover. Priced from ฿44,500,000.",
