    blurb: "A beachfront, hotel-managed investment residence by a world-famous hospitality group, set directly on Bangtao Beach at the seaside edge of Laguna Phuket. A low-rise boutique resort of just 38 apartments across four buildings, with a beach club, wellness centre and signature pools — top-floor homes have private rooftop pools. Owners earn a share of resort income plus complimentary annual stays. Off-plan, leasehold.",
    detail: "A new beachfront luxury resort by a world-famous hospitality group, set directly on Bangtao Beach in the southernmost part of Laguna Phuket — beside the developer's own Laguna Seaside and just 500 metres from the famous Catch Beach Club. It is a low-rise boutique resort comprising four residential buildings of four storeys each, with a total of only 38 exclusive apartments between them, alongside the resort's own hotel and beach club.\n\nThe homes are designed for privacy and the view: spacious living rooms open through panoramic balconies to sweeping vistas over Bangtao Beach, with only two to three units per floor. Top-floor apartments enjoy private rooftops with their own swimming pools. Layouts run from efficient one-bedrooms of 57 m² to expansive two-bedroom penthouses of up to 220 m².\n\nImportantly, this is purely an investment property rather than a conventional residence: buyers acquire a hotel unit in a professionally managed resort under a respected wellbeing-resort brand, receiving a share of the hotel's income plus complimentary stays of 30–90 days per year depending on the chosen programme — with an exchange option to use part of that allocation at the group's hotels in other countries. Resort amenities include a beach club and bar, a wellness centre, an all-day dining restaurant, a lap pool, a party pool, a jungle pool and a reflection pond, with Bangtao's own beach clubs and restaurants at your feet.\n\nThe address sits within Laguna Phuket — a 1,000-acre integrated resort in the centre of Bangtao beach, maintained to hotel standards, with seven hotels, residences, a golf course, restaurants, spas and retail galleries, plus year-round sporting and cultural events and intra-resort shuttles. Ownership carries the group's signature privileges — Sanctuary Club membership, Laguna Golf membership, and the rare offer of developer financing. Completion expected 2027, offered leasehold — priced from ฿16,670,000.",
