    detail: "This rare beachfront villa at Bang Por is a modern seaside residence on Koh Samui's tranquil, low-density north coast — positioned directly on the sand for uninterrupted ocean access and a front-row tropical lifestyle that is increasingly hard to secure. Built in 2023 on a generous 770 m² plot, it pairs contemporary design with privacy, space and immediate beach access for luxury living or premium investment.\n\nThe single-storey home offers roughly 209 m² of built area, thoughtfully designed to maximise beachfront views and indoor-outdoor flow: three bedrooms and three bathrooms plus a flexible multipurpose room that works as an office, guest room or storage. Open-plan living connects seamlessly to the patio and garden, with a striking 14-metre private pool running parallel to the shoreline as the centrepiece, and built-in furniture throughout for a clean, low-maintenance aesthetic.\n\nBeyond the pool terrace, a landscaped beachfront garden preserves open sea views while adding privacy, and a decorative koi pond brings a calming natural note. Maid's quarters, private parking, government utilities and security round out a turnkey, fully furnished home — with Maenam, Nathon, international schools and the airport all within easy reach of one of Samui's most sought-after quiet beachfront enclaves.",
