    detail: "This extraordinary five-bedroom estate is one of the most exclusive residential offerings in Chaweng Noi — set on a generous 1,600 m² plot with an impressive ~2,700 m² of built area, elevated above the coastline to capture sweeping sea views and a lush mountain backdrop. The scale, location and amenities place it firmly within the top tier of Koh Samui real estate, equally suited to a private family compound, a prestige holiday residence or a hospitality-style investment.\n\nThe architecture blends indoor luxury with expansive outdoor living: five bedrooms and eleven bathrooms give exceptional flexibility for family, guests and staff, while large open-plan living areas are positioned to capture both sea and mountain views in dramatic, light-filled volumes. Multiple leisure zones elevate it to a true resort — a spectacular 20-metre infinity-edge pool over the ocean, a separate children's pool, and a unique natural jacuzzi rock pool integrated into the landscape.\n\nWellness runs deep, with a dedicated spa area and massage room rarely found in private residences, alongside both Western and Thai kitchens for daily living and large-scale entertaining. Equipped with government electricity and deep-well water and held freehold under Chanote title, it sits minutes from Chaweng Noi's beaches, international schools, hospitals and the airport while remaining private on its hillside setting.",
