    blurb: "A six-bedroom hilltop villa in the scenic Bophut Hills, with a sunrise-to-sunset panorama over Samui's northern shore and Koh Phangan — a 25-metre infinity pool, Thai sala, cathedral-ceiling living, and a resident chef and villa manager.",
    detail: "A tropical hilltop paradise in the scenic Bophut Hills, just a 15–20 minute drive from Koh Samui International Airport. The six-bedroom villa is strategically positioned for a breathtaking sunrise-to-sunset panorama over Samui's pristine northern shore and the enchanting Koh Phangan — 'Full Moon Island' — on the horizon. Secluded and serene, it remains surprisingly close to key destinations: around 10 minutes to Fisherman's Village and 15 minutes to the vibrant lifestyle of Chaweng.\n\nEach of the six bedrooms is designed for comfort and style with its own private sea-view terrace, and recent renovations have introduced a lighter, more contemporary ambiance throughout. The living and dining space, crowned by a soaring cathedral ceiling, serves as a spectacular social hub — overlooking the 25-metre infinity-edge pool, a traditional Thai-style sala and the mesmerising sea beyond.\n\nThe experience is elevated by a dedicated team, including an experienced multilingual villa manager and a resident chef, alongside an internal elevator, gym, sauna, jacuzzi, spa room and kids' room. From culinary delights to personalised service, it is a polished, turnkey hilltop retreat for families or groups seeking the epitome of private villa living on Koh Samui.",
