    detail: "Noble Emmerse Phrom Phong offers a rare balance of artistic living and urban convenience. A 55-storey high-rise of 358 residences, the tower is composed for a life of calm refinement amidst the vibrant energy of Sukhumvit — interiors of travertine, warm timber and sculptural light that feel more gallery than lobby.\n\nIts position is the quiet luxury here. The residence sits within easy reach of the EM District — Emporium and EmQuartier — and the green of Benchasiri Park, moments from BTS Phrom Phong, and surrounded by international schools, world-class hospitals and five-star hotels.\n\nLife unfolds across distinct amenity levels. The ground floor holds the Exotique Lobby, a Greenery Retreat and a Grab & Go station; the fourth floor gathers the Aqua Serene Pool, Emmerse Cocoon Spa, gym, Pilates studio and a cinema lounge; and high on the fifty-first floor, the Mystique Social Club, Sky Lounge, private dining and the Urban Sky Lawn open to the city skyline.\n\nResidences range from efficient one-bedrooms of around 30 m² to expansive penthouses of up to 521 m². An automated parking building of nineteen levels provides approximately 90% parking capacity. Off-plan, with completion expected in Q3 2030 — priced from ฿8,260,000.",
